<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000507/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Course evaluation on regular period.
The students must follow the seminars scheduled during the sessions. They must write a summary of each presentation. The evaluation of these reports allow the student to obtain 40% of the final mark
The students must propose an innovative IoT project . During the development the students must schedule 3 millestones.
* Millestone 1: 10%. The students presents the project they want to develop. They receive a feedback from the professors
* Millestone 2: 20%. The students present the state of the art and competitors (written document and presentation)
* Millestone 3: 30%. Technical challegues and budget (written document and presentation)

Final Evaluation System and Extra exam
Each student individually must develop a complete project, write the proposal and present the project to professors. The weight is 100%"""@es ;
    ns1:hasEvaluationTrial <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/593000507/2025-26/evaluation/trial1>,
